msgid "Perfect Home was founded with a singular vision: to bring the world's finest home goods and interior products to Uzbekistan's most discerning homeowners and designers."
msgstr "Perfect Home bitta maqsad bilan tashkil etilgan: dunyoning eng sara uy va interyer mahsulotlarini O‘zbekistondagi talabchan mijozlarga olib kelish."

msgid "We believe that the objects we surround ourselves with shape how we feel, think, and live. That's why we partner exclusively with brands that share our uncompromising standards for quality, craftsmanship, and design."
msgstr "Bizni o‘rab turgan buyumlar kayfiyatimiz va hayot tarzimizni belgilaydi deb hisoblaymiz. Shu sababli faqat sifat, mahorat va dizayn bo‘yicha yuksak talablarimizga mos brendlar bilan ishlaymiz."

msgid "From Italian furniture icons to Scandinavian lighting innovators, every product in our catalog has been carefully selected by our team of design experts."
msgstr "Italiya mebel ikonalaridan Skandinaviya yoritish innovatorlarigacha — katalogimizdagi har bir mahsulot dizayn ekspertlari tomonidan sinchiklab tanlangan."

